com.adidas.connect.ui.fragment

Class EntryFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • Fragment
      • com.adidas.connect.ui.basemvp.BaseFragment<EntryFragmentContract.IEntryPresenter>
        • com.adidas.connect.ui.fragment.EntryFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBaseView, EntryFragmentContract.IEntryView

    public class EntryFragment
extends BaseFragment<EntryFragmentContract.IEntryPresenter>
implements EntryFragmentContract.IEntryView
    First access point for an user. User can request flow with email, where actions will be performed by other fragments, or start interaction with social networks. In this last case communication with social network is managed here, as long as all the possible steps not requiring user input.
